                     <interp inst="t17990109-32-verdict195" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> 
                  <rs id="t17990109-32-punish196" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990109-32-punish196" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990109-32-defend269 t17990109-32-punish196"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 31.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner was recommended to mercy by the Jury.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
